  "remarks": "TAi.146 A leader of the Haqqani Network (TE.H.12.12.), which operates out of North Waziristan in the Federally Administered Tribal Areas of Pakistan. Son of Jalaluddin Haqqani (TI.H.40.01). Has travelled to Saudi Arabia and the United Arab Emirates to raise funds for the Taliban. Reportedly deceased as of 2013.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 19 July 2010  (amended on 29 July 2011, 18 May 2012 , 22 April 2013 and 27 Jun. 2013, 11 Feb 2014).",
